@malloch_brown.https://democracyjournal.org/magazine/62-special-issue/democracies-great-challenge-demonstrating-competence/ …Kiitos. Käytämme tätä aikajanasi parantamiseen. KumoaKumoa -
From our Democracy Special Issue with
@AspenStrategy,@Joe_Nye says: "Relations with China are now at their lowest point in nearly 50 years." The question is: How do we sketch a realistic strategy toward China that also employs the soft power of democracy?https://democracyjournal.org/magazine/62-special-issue/the-united-states-china-and-democracy/ …Kiitos. Käytämme tätä aikajanasi parantamiseen. KumoaKumoa -
Read the latest
@AspenStrategy Group and@DemJournal publication, which covers the many challenges facing democracy, both at home and abroad. I authored “Democracy in a Time of Coronavirus” on the importance of a strong social contract:https://bit.ly/33d0Zr7Kiitos. Käytämme tätä aikajanasi parantamiseen. KumoaKumoa -
As the
#SummitforDemocracy continues today, learn more about the global democratic decline, the authoritarian challenge from China, and the state of democracy in America by reading “Democracy’s Future: Abroad and at Home” from ASG and@DemJournalhttps://bit.ly/33d0Zr7Kiitos. Käytämme tätä aikajanasi parantamiseen. KumoaKumoa -
Today is the first day of the
@StateDept’s#SummitForDemocracy. Learn more about the challenges facing democracy by reading ASG and@DemJournal’s new publication “Democracy’s Future: Abroad and at Home,” including@abramowitz’s essay on authoritarianism. https://bit.ly/3ICblRu pic.twitter.com/nqCZSsV2dvKiitos. Käytämme tätä aikajanasi parantamiseen. KumoaKumoa -
