"Why can't we have nice things?" That's the opening line of
@hmcghee's The Sum of Us, which is on my personal top ten list of books for the year. I quote it and apply her solidarity argument in a new piece in@DemJournal https://democracyjournal.org/magazine/62-special-issue/renewing-american-democracy/ …,@AspenStrategyKiitos. Käytämme tätä aikajanasi parantamiseen. KumoaKumoa -
